   Welcome to GNUnet Planetlab Largescale Management Tool (gplmt)


Features to implement
===============

- Parallel tasks
- Monitor mode
- Console mode
- Implement curses based logger

Known Bugs 
===============
- SFTP does not work in PlanetLab nodes
- Have to throttle parallelism due to "Too many open files" issue

Implemented in
===============

revision 22775: Change task description language to better represent different operations
revision 22784: SFTP put and get operations
revision 22789: PlanetLab API support to retrieve nodes assigned to slice
